children.subject: Is there any update about this class?

history.content:
As other classes are shuffled around we realized that we need to temporarily close enrollment for CS 195 as we wait to see if the day/time/instructor are impacted by other changes.

Please note: We use Department Consent to indicate that a class is CLOSED. If you email asking for permission to get into the class, we will not grant it. Please keep checking classes.berkeley.edu to see when the hold is removed and the class re-opens for enrollment.

I apologize for any inconvenience this change causes.
